text:
The Interview magazine called the Kardashians the first family, with Kim being the first woman of the U.S.

Kim Kardashian appears on the September cover of the magazine with a Jackie Kennedy-inspired look as she poses next to her daughter North West. This is the first time little North appeared on a magazine cover.

Inside the publication, there is a Kim and North photoshoot in a space that looks similar to the White House. They both got their own separate interviews – another first time for the little one.
title: Kim Kardashian Dubbed “America’s New First Lady” on First Magazine Cover With North West
